{"tid":632952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨有心搞死達哥同蘋果日報其實唔難","createTime":"2018-04-18T01:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T15:21:58.000Z","uid":31637,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6095315a50613fc74628d33d87617076c2dc44d3","tid":632952,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:20:03.000Z","msg":"用錢請達哥不停玩D完全冇人想睇既GAME, 搞臭達哥個朵<br />\n<br />\n派D高(假)學歷間諜低薪入去蘋果日報做記者編輯, 不停出埋D假新聞, 做臭蘋果日報個朵<br />\n<br />\n要搞死任何一個有影響力既人或媒體,其實一D都唔難"},{"pid":"73aa0b57c7c0bfcfa2d73f74fa26a8f8fe8273a0","tid":632952,"uid":156005,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:23:48.000Z","msg":"蘋果其實都已經好多亂鳩黎既新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733827a523764e830fdf6079cef95115a348e797","tid":632952,"uid":92498,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:25:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40601868f2a34eea548ef758d06c80a2571b805a","tid":632952,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:26:50.000Z","msg":"呢個方法比起養班冇人睇既奶共報紙更加有效率同更加低成本<br />\n<br />\n連錢都唔洗點燒, 就可以搞掂香港輿論"},{"pid":"f5ff7ab039677500ed6a2fb7802a1377c86f714c","tid":632952,"uid":43412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:30:16.000Z","msg":"係你嘅世界係咪冇拒絕同埋解僱？"},{"pid":"cadefe328674ec70262e05ba390fd49b053c01de","tid":632952,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5ff7ab039677500ed6a2fb7802a1377c86f714c","tid":632952,"uid":43412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:30:16.000Z","msg":"係你嘅世界係咪冇拒絕同埋解僱？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:32:15.000Z","msg":"如果呢個世界牛永遠唔洗飲水就係囉"},{"pid":"656635d6f487bd87eb69af5d3adda34f6f69737d","tid":632952,"uid":27688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T01:35:27.000Z","msg":"睇蘋果用字愈來愈中國化就知<br />\n又小三 又話語權 又落戶xx 又首席執行官 又折騰"},{"pid":"2acab27adc1cf0a0ae6d2f891c8caf6a48ce8d1c","tid":632952,"uid":31637,"like":0,